00:13:42.721 --> 00:13:44.590 line:95%,end
<i>I think Mackenzie's dance is darling.</i>

00:13:44.657 --> 00:13:47.526 line:95%,end
The difficulty level is right up there.

00:13:47.593 --> 00:13:48.861 line:95%,end
Knee, ball change.

